{"type": "article", "id": 25003, "title": "倾斜的边桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-06T07:18:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607113531J87rDlasqyLbSAdE.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是 Nendo 最新推出的大理石边桌，有高低两种，桌面和桌腿方正却都是向着左或右倾斜，从正面看是一个平行四边形，给人一种快要塌下来的错觉。设计师想要探索大理石材料的轻盈和灵活。桌子有黑白两色，是为意大利品牌 Marsotto edizioni 而设计，即将在米兰家具展上展出。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113528VHNxh1RaCv37Lw54.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113528TM0nGwY7Xbvgji8u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113529UzZ9NOj2tFcqsMTJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113529C9Mq6HIxi4hyKGaE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607113530UMbvTdtWQHa5Ycjz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66773504\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071135302fohJPGsAZXL7y16.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63995726\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}